-- =====================================================
-- Arkansas (AR) Medical Malpractice Rules
-- Enhanced Verification Protocol v2.0
-- =====================================================
-- State: Arkansas
-- Governing Law: Ark. Code § 16-114-201 et seq. (Medical Injury Actions)
-- Negligence Model: MODIFIED COMPARATIVE FAULT — 50% bar (Ark. Code § 16-64-122)
-- SOL: 2 years from act (§ 16-114-203); foreign object: 1 year from discovery
-- Damage Caps: $500,000 non-economic cap (Arkansas Amendment 94, 2018)
-- Expert: Required per Ark. Code § 16-114-207 (Ark. R. Evid. Rule 702)
-- Punitive: Capped at greater of $250,000 or 3x compensatory, max $1M (§ 16-55-208)
-- =====================================================

-- RULE 1: STANDARD OF CARE
